<br>
Our group is currently in the high 30s and low 40s range and we are seeking someone in the same experience range. We currently have within our group: Troll Shadow Knight (myself), Vah Shir Bard (evilly aligned), Dark Elf Wizard, Dark Elf Cleric. We also have been quite lucky as of late to adventure alongside a very capable Dark Elven Mage. <br>
<br>
We are very family oriented and act almost like a mini guild together. We prefer to maintain an RP environment but do occasionally have our OOC moments. None of our number owe their allegiance to any official guild at the moment. We do a great deal of hunting on Kunark specifically, though we do travel with ease between the new portals from the Plane of Knowledge and having a wizard in our company. In Velious our group are Kromriff mercenaries, allied to all giants and enemies of the Coldain Dwarves and Dragons. <br>
<br>
If you are an experienced enchanter/enchantress who is looking for a steady group to adventure with (hunt, roleplay, enjoy good company) for the next 20 seasons or so, please give me a shout in game. I will be happy to answer and questions you may have and we can make arrangements to hunt together and see how it goes. <br>
<br>
